Diana DASENT, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Todd KOPPEL, M.D., Garden State Pain Management, and Clifton Surgery Center, Defendants-Respondents. C-462 September Term 2017
080199 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 12, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005328-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
